abstract: Dutch cyclist Wouter Poels wins Tour of Catalonia’s fifth stage, but trails overall leader Nairo Quintana.

headline.main: Wouter Poels Wins in Tour of Catalonia’s Fifth Stage

snippet: The Dutch rider Wouter Poels broke away to win the Tour of Catalonia’s fifth stage, while Nairo Quintana defended his overall lead.
lead_paragraph: The Dutch rider Wouter Poels broke away to win the Tour of Catalonia’s fifth stage, while Nairo Quintana defended his overall lead.
